remarks.para:
The JSON schema emitted for each event is a compact, flat JSON line intended for hot-path processing. Each line represents a single trade or quote object:
{"timestamp":"…","symbol":"SPY","price":100.01,"size":200,"aggressor":1,"sequence":42}
Quote events follow a similar shape with bid/ask-specific fields. This schema is specific to the hot-path pipeline and does not include the higher-level MarketEvent envelope (such as type or payload).
